Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:18.36,Lucy-Song-Title,,0,0,0,,[I want to be a rainbow]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:29.82,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa hoshifuru yoru ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:36.75,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono tomoshibi wo keshi wa shinai to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:47.88,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa akane no asa ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:56.81,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wakaba ni somaru haru wo yobou to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:01:08.70,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Ono utsu hibiki michi hiraku utagoe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:20.59,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kodama ga mune ni hazunde kuru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:26.43,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono oosora no niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:36.23,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kibou ni todoku niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:29.82,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow I made on that starry night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:36.75,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To not let this flame die
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:47.88,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow made on that brilliant red morning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:56.81,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To call out for spring, dyed with young leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:01:08.70,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Cutting axes open up roads, under the sound of singing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:20.59,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,The echoes bounce around in my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:26.43,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow in this big sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:36.23,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow that reaches out to hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.97,0:01:47.86,Lucy-Ep-Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,306.667)\fade(300,336)}Ep. 48 - Becoming a Well-Off Child...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:20.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's about my family, you hear?!\NWe're moving to live on a farm!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:23.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.13,0:02:25.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Our family is moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.39,0:02:27.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, well that's a shame, Tob.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:31.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to see that farm tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:33.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.41,0:02:36.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to see the farm tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:39.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? It's a great thing that you managed to buy a farm!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.75,0:02:42.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.96,0:02:44.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.33,0:02:48.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't buy no farm!\NIt's Mr. Princeton's farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:51.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So Mr. Princeton bought it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:53.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No he didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:03:01.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it pretty?\NI wanna be a blacksmith too.
Comment: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:03.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:06.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:12.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So dad decided to work at Mr. Princeton's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.37,0:03:14.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We're going there to go see that farm tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:17.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you need to hire a carriage somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.04,0:03:21.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No. Mr. Princeton will show us around\Non his own carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:23.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? That's pretty impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:25.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you coming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.69,0:03:30.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose. Since it's a farm that dad is gonna work at,\Nand also the place where you guys are gonna move to,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.51,0:03:32.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,it'd be better for me to see it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:34.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But you won't be living there yourself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:37.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Dad is the one who's been hired, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:40.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Clara, won't be living with us on the farm either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:41.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:43.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Because she's getting married!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.10,0:03:49.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Dad finally gave them his permission,\Nso she's moving to live here with John?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:54.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't wanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:04:01.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Just because you'll be made to attend school at Princeton's Farm, you don't want to move now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.25,0:04:05.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That too. But if I stay here, I'll be made\Nto go to school anyway, so it's all the same to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.63,0:04:09.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say that I don't wanna move to the farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:14.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad and mom are actually delighted\Nto be moving to Princeton's Farm soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:15.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:16.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.97,0:04:22.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Even though that farm won't belong to us, Mr. Princeton\Npromised to run it according to dad's advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:24.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That much, I know myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:27.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why, then, are you so bristled up against it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:30.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Our family is getting scattered all across the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:35.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're making a mountain of a molehill.\NIt's only Clara and Ben that we'll have to part with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:37.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,John too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:40.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?\NJohn isn't our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:45.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But after he marries Clara,\Nwon't he become a brother in law to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:47.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He'd be like family to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:49.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:54.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wish there was a place\Nwhere our whole family could live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.80,0:04:58.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But Ben is currently working\Nat the customs office in the harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:00.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He can only occasionally turn up home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:02.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And that he does, every Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:07.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But after we move to Princeton's Farm,\Nit'll be too far away for him to be coming there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:10.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little, you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:16.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be done soon. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:21.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.97,0:05:23.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Really? That sure was quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:27.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So you came to let us know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:31.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be really nice if you could talk too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.03,0:05:36.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:38.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back. Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:41.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's always the same story with you, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:43.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:46.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a child anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:51.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Greeting me with "Are you hungry, are you hungry?" whenever I return home is a thing from my childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.57,0:05:56.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say so. You've only stopped\Nbeing a child recently. So, are you hungry or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:06:00.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I am kinda hungry.\NBut I can wait until everyone else gathers for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:03.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Welcome back, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:05.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:06.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I just came.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:08.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good job, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:11.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Is that fresh goat milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.61,0:06:14.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is. Sticky's and Pansy's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.34,0:06:16.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, can I have some too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:25.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, do you think this map is precise?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:27.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Well, it'll do for giving me a general idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:30.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I went to the surveying office\Nand copied the one they had.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:34.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This thick line marks the borders\Nof Princeton's Farm, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.32,0:06:34.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:37.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It looks pretty vast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:39.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's about 100 acres or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:41.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? 100 acres?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:42.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:46.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not only they're growing crops there,\Nthey also keep cows and sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:49.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, some land that's yet to be\Ndeveloped for cultivating.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:52.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they'd be willing to share\Nat least a bit of that cheap land.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.39,0:06:58.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In your hands, even that land\Ncan be turned into a thriving field, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:06:58.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:07:04.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If we get a chance to build a farm of your own design,\NI'd also quit my customs job and come to work with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.45,0:07:05.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,John would be happy to help too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:09.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben, this won't be my farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:12.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be working for the good of Mr. Princeton's farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.31,0:07:17.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know all the details,\Nbut it's clear that the farm needs rebuilding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:22.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to work on it alone,\NI wonder if you even can pull that rebuilding off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:27.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Princeton assured me that he doesn't have any problem with running the farm according to my vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:29.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:34.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,the manager of that farm, as well as other workers would probably be delighted at you joining them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:38.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I thought about it plenty myself and concluded that the only way to know is by giving it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:42.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see. In that case, I don't have to say anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.09,0:07:47.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, I'm going with you to see that farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:07.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sleepy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:09.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:12.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what Princeton's Farm would be like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:14.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. I'm sure it's so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:17.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right about {\i1}what{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:21.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be taking a lunch with us tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:24.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're not really following what I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:26.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good night if so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.39,0:08:28.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You can sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:29.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:31.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What a strange girl you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:37.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The place we're visiting tomorrow\Nwould soon become our home for quite a long while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:40.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Clara is going with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:42.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I know Ben said he wants to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:46.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'll come with John.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:49.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.29,0:08:51.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:52.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:57.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Princeton probably has\Na very comfortable carriage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:00.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder, exactly how much people it can fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:04.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried that Clara and John\Nwould have to ride standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.09,0:09:06.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:09.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You rode that carriage many times,\Nso you oughta know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:10.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I'm sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.89,0:09:13.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? What was that? What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:26.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Fast asleep already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:31.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what time it is now, even.
Comment: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:34.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:41.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in trouble. I'm not sleepy at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:13.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, come out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.30,0:10:29.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you lay just a bit more?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, good morning, Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:41.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy. Kate didn't wake up yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:43.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:46.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We won't be able to take Little along today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:50.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he wants to see it too.\NOur future home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.49,0:10:54.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's so far, it's not easy for a horse\Nto pull the carriage all the way to Princeton's Farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.91,0:10:58.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Princeton's carriage runs under two horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:06.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate. Kate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.50,0:11:09.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up already!\NHow long are you gonna sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:12.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still sleepy!\NLeave me along for a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.41,0:11:16.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you wanna stay and watch the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.33,0:11:17.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Watch the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:20.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Princeton will come to pick us up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:24.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to see the farm today, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:26.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:28.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Say, you've had your breakfast already?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.69,0:11:31.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is waiting for you at the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.03,0:11:34.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Why didn't you wake me up earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.33,0:11:37.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?\NI tried to wake you up time and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.49,0:11:38.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:45.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder when will Mr. Princeton arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:48.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't settle on any certain hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:50.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,but well, it'll be around 10 o'clock I reckon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:53.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If so, we've no time to spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.50,0:11:58.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for oversleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:12:00.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder since when are you such a late sleeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.89,0:12:02.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's a special case today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.35,0:12:06.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about going to the farm all night long\Nand lost my sleep completely to excitement.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.30,0:12:10.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,All right, that's settled.\NShall we start eating now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:11.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.22,0:12:18.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why is Little barking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Probably someone is at the doorstep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.69,0:12:23.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me Mr. Princeton showed up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.79,0:12:25.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Should I go check?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.30,0:12:38.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Max, Mr. Princeton's coachman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.39,0:12:44.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, truly, I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.00,0:12:46.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We have just started eating the breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:50.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll try to be done with it at once,\Nso if you could ask Mr. Princeton to wait inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:52.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.90,0:12:55.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But then, inside the carriage...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:57.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Master didn't come in that carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:13:01.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the Madam suddenly fell ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:04.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So Master found himself unable to leave the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.79,0:13:06.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The Madam is ill?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.62,0:13:10.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Therefore, Master stayed by her side to nurse her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:12.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... So that's what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.92,0:13:18.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's why Master sent me here to let you know that he'd like to give you an excursion on some other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:20.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:24.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That is all. Pardon the intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:26.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:35.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Can't help it if his wife is ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:39.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He said "some other day" but which day it would be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.41,0:13:40.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:44.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He spoke with a great deal of uncertainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:07.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:14.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Max has just returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:15.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:18.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He reported delivering your message\Nexactly as you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:21.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Tell Max I appreciate his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.30,0:14:22.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.76,0:14:23.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.95,0:14:26.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The other party seemed\Nconsiderably upset with the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:28.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:29.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If you excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.31,0:14:36.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There you heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:40.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I had to cancel my excursion through the farm\Nfor Mr. Popple today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.11,0:14:44.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But please listen well. Whatever it takes,\NI set my mind on putting that farm straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.39,0:14:46.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If you, who had managed the farm up to now,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:50.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,happen to have any solid idea\Nabout what to do next, I'd like to hear it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:53.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to do it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:57.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But remember, I can't keep Mr. Popple waiting forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.53,0:15:01.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, in two or three days at most,\NI'd like to hear what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:26.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:27.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:32.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If your fever is gone, don't you think\Nit'll be better for you to get up and move a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:33.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:34.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:35.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I saw a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:36.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.44,0:15:37.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The same dream as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:39.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. About having a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:43.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. About playing around with a lovely girl.
Comment: 0,0:15:43.91,0:15:45.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:52.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The weather is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.65,0:15:53.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:15:58.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,All I want is for you to get better soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.31,0:16:03.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I had a trip to the farm\Nwith the Popples arranged for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:05.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,With Lucy as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.64,0:16:11.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Since Mr. Popple decided to work at the farm,\Nhe's also taking his family there with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:14.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But you didn't go to the farm? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.90,0:16:17.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I let Pepys handle the farm for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:21.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But he said he's against Mr. Popple\Ncoming to take the reins there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:23.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you dismiss Pepys, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:25.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.07,0:16:29.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But you want to assign Mr. Popple\Nto do Pepys's job, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:32.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I would probably end up doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:36.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You can't question Mr. Popple's enthusiasm\Nin the matters of running a farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:38.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:43.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Her father made it all the way to Southern Australia\Nin order to build a farm of his own.
Comment: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:45.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:46.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.46,0:16:48.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:52.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. If you do that,\Nthings are destined to go well!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:55.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Sylvia?\NWhat is destined to go well?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:16:57.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's it... That's just it, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:58.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:03.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please, dear. Give a piece of land to Mr. Popple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:05.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:07.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what land it'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:11.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Your farm in Gawler has plenty of land\Nstill waiting to be reclaimed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.27,0:17:12.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That land...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.18,0:17:15.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sylvia, can you even hear what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:23.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.21,0:17:24.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:29.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Last night, I was so excited about going\Nto that farm today, I couldn't get any sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:34.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I also wanted to go see it today.\NToo bad, but now I won't be able to do it with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:38.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Madam's illness really is that serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:40.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She always seemed to be a sturdy person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:44.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But if it's really bad, you probably\Ngotta go check on her, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:46.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,After all, Madam dotes on you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.84,0:17:51.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem like Mr. Princeton will come to visit us\Nany time soon, so I might as well do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.53,0:17:53.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'm coming along too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:55.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No need, I can handle it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.13,0:17:57.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure? It's a long way to Northern Adelaide.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:17:59.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:04.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But it's really best that I come along.\NYou're too absentminded, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:05.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.71,0:18:07.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's always the same song with you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:19.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you two.\NDon't quarrel over some petty things again, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.58,0:18:21.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:23.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't my fault either!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:24.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.67,0:18:28.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one only ever thinking about yourself here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:30.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, look who's talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:32.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break, you two!
Comment: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:34.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:37.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, just do whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:40.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.27,0:18:42.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Giddyup!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.48,0:18:44.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Ben!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.61,0:18:46.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come back next week too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:54.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:56.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Ben!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:57.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.41,0:18:59.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:01.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.70,0:19:13.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it isn't too soon yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.51,0:19:18.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But if we wait any longer, we might end up\Nmoving to the farm before harvesting them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:21.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you go there ahead of everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:25.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know yet, though I considered that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.21,0:19:29.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But even if you go there,\Nyou'll still attend my wedding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.13,0:19:30.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:33.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Look, when it'll be time for dancing at the reception,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:37.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,you could do it even here, at this very field.\NAfter we've taken out all the potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.12,0:19:39.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You won't use it for anything else after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.29,0:19:42.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather leave that headache\Nto whoever buys this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.01,0:19:50.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I always wondered, what it's like\Nto ride a marvelous carriage like that of Mr. Princeton.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:52.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Better stop thinking about such trifles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:57.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You only say that because you rode it\NGod knows how many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.17,0:20:00.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And I've never even approached\Na two-horse carriage in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.41,0:20:03.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess we'll get to ride it\Nwhen we go to the farm next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:06.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He'll come on a different carriage next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.88,0:20:07.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're so mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:21.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, little ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.69,0:20:32.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Then, I really don't mind giving you two\Na leisure ride on this carriage today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:35.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really need it. Only Kate does.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.20,0:20:36.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather you ride it too, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:42.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I'll be having a very important talk\Nwith your father and mother now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:45.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:47.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.51,0:20:49.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.71,0:20:50.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.44,0:20:53.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Max, drive them around the area for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.88,0:20:54.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:57.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little, you wait for us here. Okay, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.91,0:21:21.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He's washing his hands right now.\NHe just finished harvesting the potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:26.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm truly sorry for letting you down\Non our arrangements for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.78,0:21:39.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:43.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.89,0:21:54.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You silly thing.\NDidn't I tell you to stay home and wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:22:00.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for the delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.80,0:22:04.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No need. I'm the one truly at fault\Nfor what happened in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.60,0:22:07.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How is your wife's condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.09,0:22:10.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate your concern for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.10,0:22:12.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotten considerably better since.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.08,0:22:13.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.08,0:22:17.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So, when will you give us a tour through the farm?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.80,0:22:21.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I still can't say for sure, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.77,0:22:24.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, a small circumstance came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.28,0:22:29.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that my employment\Nhas to be canceled?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.63,0:22:32.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. It's anything but that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:35.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I'm still putting my deepest trust in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:37.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.81,0:22:39.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? Please say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.70,0:23:18.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, I'm not sure\Nif I can muster enough courage to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.72,0:23:22.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't feel shy.\NWhatever it may be, say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.19,0:23:25.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If so, I'll put it bluntly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.71,0:23:29.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Could you let us adopt Lucy as our own daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.32,0:23:34.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Adopt, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.61,0:23:35.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.99,0:23:38.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural that you're so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.77,0:23:42.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,For a matter like this, you'll need\Nto consult with your wife thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.44,0:23:46.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We'd like to bring Lucy up as our own child.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.15,0:23:55.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We'd like to adopt Lucy, by all means.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.50,0:24:06.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Next episode of "Lucy-May of the Southern Rainbow":\NClara's Wedding
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.44,0:24:05.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: "Clara's Wedding".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.37,0:24:06.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
